    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Receba pagamentos por Boleto banc\u00e1rio, Pix, Cart\u00e3o de Cr\u00e9dito e Open Finance em sua loja WooCommerce com a Ef\u00ed Bank.<\/p>\n<h3>Descri\u00e7\u00e3o<\/h3>\n<p>Este \u00e9 o Plugin Oficial fornecido pela <a href=\"https:\/\/sejaefi.com.br\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Ef\u00ed Bank<\/a> para WooCommerce. Com ele, o propriet\u00e1rio da loja pode optar por receber pagamentos por Boleto Banc\u00e1rio, Cart\u00e3o de Cr\u00e9dito, Pix ou Open Finance. Todo processo \u00e9 realizado por meio do checkout transparente. Com isso, o comprador n\u00e3o precisa sair do site da loja para efetuar o pagamento.<\/p>\n<p>Caso voc\u00ea tenha alguma d\u00favida ou sugest\u00e3o, entre em contato conosco pelo site <a href=\"https:\/\/sejaefi.com.br\/fale-conosco\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Clicando AQUI<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>Requisitos<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Vers\u00e3o do PHP: 7.x ou superior<\/li>\n<li>Vers\u00e3o do WooCommerce: 5.x ou superior<\/li>\n<li>Vers\u00e3o do WordPress: 6.x ou superior<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Instala\u00e7\u00e3o autom\u00e1tica<\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Acesse o link em sua loja &#8220;Plugins&#8221; -&gt; &#8220;Adicionar novo&#8221; -&gt; No campo de busca, pesquise por &#8220;Ef\u00ed Bank&#8221;.<\/li>\n<li>Clique em &#8220;Instalar agora&#8221;.<\/li>\n<li>Ap\u00f3s a instala\u00e7\u00e3o, clique em &#8220;Ativar o Plugin&#8221;.<\/li>\n<li>Configure o plugin em &#8220;WooCommerce&#8221; &gt; &#8220;Configura\u00e7\u00f5es&#8221; &gt; &#8220;Pagamentos&#8221;  e comece a receber pagamentos!<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3>Configura\u00e7\u00e3o<\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Ative o plugin.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Configure as credenciais de sua Aplica\u00e7\u00e3o. Para criar uma nova Aplica\u00e7\u00e3o, entre em sua conta Ef\u00ed Bank, acesse o menu &#8220;API&#8221; e clique em &#8220;Aplica\u00e7\u00f5es&#8221; -&gt; &#8220;Nova aplica\u00e7\u00e3o&#8221;. Libere os escopos desejados e ent\u00e3o insira as credenciais Client ID e Client Secret de produ\u00e7\u00e3o e homologa\u00e7\u00e3o nos respectivos campos de configura\u00e7\u00e3o do plugin.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Configure as op\u00e7\u00f5es de pagamento que deseja receber: Boleto, Cart\u00e3o de Cr\u00e9dito, Open Finance e\/ou Pix.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Caso utilize a op\u00e7\u00e3o de Cart\u00e3o de Cr\u00e9dito:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Insira o Identificador de Conta de sua conta Ef\u00ed Bank.<br \/>\nPara encontrar o Identificador, entre em sua conta, acesse o menu &#8220;API&#8221; e clique em &#8220;Introdu\u00e7\u00e3o&#8221;. Na lateral direita haver\u00e1 um bot\u00e3o chamado &#8220;Identificador de conta&#8221; basta clicar e o c\u00f3digo identificador ser\u00e1 exibido<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Caso utilize a op\u00e7\u00e3o de Pix:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Insira sua Chave Pix cadastrada em sua conta Ef\u00ed.<\/li>\n<li>Insira o seu certificado (arquivo .p12).<\/li>\n<li>Marque o campo &#8220;Validar mTLS&#8221; caso deseje utilizar a valida\u00e7\u00e3o mTLS em seu servidor.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Caso utilize a op\u00e7\u00e3o de Open Finance:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Insira seu CPF\/CNPJ (APENAS N\u00daMEROS)<\/li>\n<li>Nome completo<\/li>\n<li>N\u00famero da conta Ef\u00ed (Com d\u00edgito e SEM TRA\u00c7O)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Recomendamos que antes de disponibilizar os pagamentos, o lojista realize testes de cobran\u00e7a com o sandbox(ambiente de testes) ativado para verificar se o procedimento de pagamento est\u00e1 acontecendo conforme esperado.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3>**Documenta\u00e7\u00e3o Adicional**<\/h3>\n<p>A documenta\u00e7\u00e3o completa com todos os endpoints e detalhes das APIs est\u00e1 dispon\u00edvel em https:\/\/dev.efipay.com.br\/docs\/modulos\/WordPress.<\/p>\n<p>Se voc\u00ea ainda n\u00e3o tem uma conta digital Ef\u00ed Bank, <a href=\"https:\/\/sejaefi.com.br\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">abra a sua agora<\/a>!<\/p>\n<h3>**Comunidade no Discord**<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/comunidade.sejaefi.com.br\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Se voc\u00ea tem a necessidade de integrar seu sistema ou aplica\u00e7\u00e3o a uma API completa de pagamentos, desejos de trocar experi\u00eancias e compartilhar seu conhecimento, conecte-se \u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/comunidade.sejaefi.com.br\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">comunidade da Ef\u00ed no Discord<\/a>.<\/p>\n",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Problem\u00e1tico e cheio de bugs<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jadergabriel2\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/56c6f8f2014bd82126ee1c68e04c5605?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/56c6f8f2014bd82126ee1c68e04c5605?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jadergabriel2\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jadergabriel2<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 28, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O plugin funciona bem na vers\u00e3o 1.4.*, e nas vers\u00f5es 2.0 em diante est\u00e1 uma verdadeira bosta, trabalho de amador mesmo. Diz se compat\u00edvel com v\u00e1rias vers\u00f5es do WOO e n\u00e3o \u00e9. N\u00e3o funciona bem com PHP 8 e pior: debuga no checkout, que por sua vez s\u00f3 funciona as vezes e n\u00e3o processa as transa\u00e7\u00f5es. Para um plugin que \u00e9 condi\u00e7\u00e3o fic de uma loja virtual, e impedir a venda \u00e9 a pior coisa pos\u015bivel<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Vers\u00e3o Bugada<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/davidcsmti\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/299f325c3cb51778fade585662210d5a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/299f325c3cb51778fade585662210d5a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/davidcsmti\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">davidcsmti<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 15, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ap\u00f3s a nova vers\u00e3o que est\u00e1 causando v\u00e1rios problemas.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- Quando configurado que o boleto tem desconto na descri\u00e7\u00e3o do label o simbolo percentual % est\u00e1 mostrando 2 vezes.<br \/>Ficando assim: Boleto - 3%% de Desconto<br \/><br \/>- Quando tem cupom aplicado no pedido e o boleto est\u00e1 configurado para ter um valor de desconto, est\u00e1 dando erro n\u00e3o consegue finalizar o pedido.<br \/><br \/>-N\u00e3o est\u00e1 reconhecendo as mascaras do <strong>Brazilian Market on WooCommerce<\/strong><br \/><br \/>Est\u00e1 tudo desconfigurado, s\u00f3 est\u00e1 causando problema na loja.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bug na \u00faltima vers\u00e3o<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/datacaixa\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/79ec3610d93505d659f0c47574feb240?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/79ec3610d93505d659f0c47574feb240?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/datacaixa\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Datacaixa <small>(datacaixa)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 13, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O cliente n\u00e3o consegue mais comprar no site depois que atualizei o plugin GERENCIANET, n\u00e3o consegue mais digitar o CPF\/CNPJ e CEP.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Vers\u00e3o cheia de bugs<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/erihenrique\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ca16c1d1fdf93d9e1c312fcdf105173a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ca16c1d1fdf93d9e1c312fcdf105173a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/erihenrique\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">erihenrique<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 6, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Esta nova vers\u00e3o est\u00e1 entrando em conflito com o plugin <strong>Brazilian Market on WooCommerce<\/strong> impedindo a digita\u00e7\u00e3o dos campos CPF, CEP e Telefone, n\u00e3o permitindo que cliente fa\u00e7am as compras.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bugs<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/pllinformatica\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d6e700334783f13bfc0fc3bb4ba86db0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d6e700334783f13bfc0fc3bb4ba86db0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/pllinformatica\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pllinformatica<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 1, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Essa ultima atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o teve v\u00e1rios bugs. N\u00e3o estava permitindo digitar o Cep e nem o CPF, ao digitar simplesmente apagava. Outro bug \u00e9 que n\u00e3o estava formatando os campos de data de vencimento e data de nascimento do cart\u00e3o e nem estava carregando as op\u00e7\u00f5es de parcelamento.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bug na ultima atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tianoduarte0909\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b98a9875b92bc80c8abd775c4fee5d60?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b98a9875b92bc80c8abd775c4fee5d60?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tianoduarte0909\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tianoduarte0909<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 26, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Estava utilizando o Pluguin em 4 Sites, por\u00e9m essa ultima atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o teve v\u00e1rios bugs e tive que desativar. N\u00e3o estava permitindo digitar o Cep e nem o CPF, ao digitar simplesmente apagava. Outro bug \u00e9 que n\u00e3o estava formatando os campos de data de vencimento e data de nascimento do cart\u00e3o e nem estava carregando as op\u00e7\u00f5es de parcelamento.  <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugin OFICIAL N\u00c3O TRATA os dados, muito ruim!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/vsprodutos\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/44fdbf93c14fef5625eeeb2b7184801b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/44fdbf93c14fef5625eeeb2b7184801b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/vsprodutos\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vsprodutos<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 7, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Cheio de erros no checkout. \nConfigura\u00e7\u00e3o complicada para pagamentos PIX e webhook n\u00e3o funciona (o status do pedido n\u00e3o \u00e9 alterado automaticamente). Mensagens de erros avulsas durante o checkout Woocommerce. Erros sem tratamentos sendo apresentados ao usu\u00e1rio como \"cURL stopped: line 58 - name not accepted\". Lembrando: ESSE \u00c9 O PLUGIN OFICIAL!!!\n\nInfelizmente, continuarei com o Mercado Pago at\u00e9 existir algo melhor.\n\nDeixo algumas sugest\u00f5es de melhoria:\n-Possibilidade de definir o status que ter\u00e1 o pedido ap\u00f3s o pagamento.\n-Separar as op\u00e7\u00f5es de pagamento. Hoje \u00e9 tudo junto, na hora do checkout voc\u00ea escolhe: \"Cart\u00e3o de Cr\u00e9dito, Boleto ou PIX\" na mesma op\u00e7\u00e3o. E o correto seria dar a op\u00e7\u00e3o de mostrar cada forma de pagamento de forma \u00fanica no checkout e n\u00e3o tudo junto.\n-Facilitar a forma de receber um pagamento por PIX e o plugin alterar o status do pedido automaticamente. Hoje, necessita instalar certificado digital, chave p\u00fablica e uma s\u00e9rie de configura\u00e7\u00f5es no servidor. O maior concorrente, o Mercado Pago, \u00e9 t\u00e3o simples. Basta instalar o plugin, definir as chaves de API e pronto. Tudo funciona perfeitamente.\n\n <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">N\u00e3o serviu para mim<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/sergiokucera\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/cb1cbf510329a6c6182ee7e7a70a0fcb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/cb1cbf510329a6c6182ee7e7a70a0fcb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/sergiokucera\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">S\u00e9rgio Kucera - formatameupc.com.br <small>(sergiokucera)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 29, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">&lt;p&gt;Irritante pra configurar. N\u00e3o permite alterar o nome da forma de pagamento no checkout. Eu queria mudar o nome para \"Pix via Ef\u00ed - aprova\u00e7\u00e3o autom\u00e1tica\", mas n\u00e3o d\u00e1. Nos outros plugins de pagamento d\u00e1 pra fazer isso.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Tamb\u00e9m n\u00e3o tem o \u00edcone do Pix no checkout.&lt;\/p&gt;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Problemas &amp; Melhorias<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/paulodbs\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/24cb87a09732f9662c18821c31557395?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/24cb87a09732f9662c18821c31557395?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/paulodbs\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">paulodbs<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 24, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">O plugin est\u00e1 com problema na atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o autom\u00e1tica do pedido, E est\u00e1 faltando op\u00e7\u00e3o de copiar \u00e9 colar o c\u00f3digo PIX, e tem algumas coisas que est\u00e1 em Ingl\u00eas.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">M\u00f3dulo excelente<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dmalberto\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/08e9c073a98d8170ccab43124eb2be5b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/08e9c073a98d8170ccab43124eb2be5b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dmalberto\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dmalberto<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 17, 2019<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">O m\u00f3dulo se integrou muito bem com minha plataforma e meu tema. Recomendo!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
